418 static void DPC_ObjectDetection_frameStart (DPM_DPCHandle handle)
419 {
420  ObjDetObj *objDetObj = (ObjDetObj *) handle;
421 
422  objDetObj->stats.frameStartTimeStamp = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp();
423 
424  DebugP_log2("ObjDet DPC: Frame Start, frameIndx = %d, subFrameIndx = %d\n",
425  objDetObj->stats.frameStartIntCounter, objDetObj->subFrameIndx);
426 
427  /* Check if previous frame (sub-frame) processing has completed */
428  DPC_Objdet_Assert(objDetObj->dpmHandle, (objDetObj->interSubFrameProcToken == 0));

431  /* Increment interrupt counter for debugging and reporting purpose */

436

438  DebugP_assert (DPM_notifyExecute (objDetObj->dpmHandle, handle, true) == 0);
439  return;

460 static void DPC_ObjDet_quadFit(float *x, float*y, float *xv, float *yv)
461 {
462  float a, b, c, denom;
463  float x0 = x[0];
464  float x1 = x[1];
465  float x2 = x[2];
466  float y0 = y[0];
467  float y1 = y[1];
468  float y2 = y[2];
469 
470  denom = (x0 - x1)*(x0 - x2)*(x1 - x2);
471  a = (x2 * (y1 - y0) + x1 * (y0 - y2) + x0 * (y2 - y1)) / denom;
472  b = (x2*x2 * (y0 - y1) + x1*x1 * (y2 - y0) + x0*x0 * (y1 - y2)) / denom;
473  c = (x1 * x2 * (x1 - x2) * y0 + x2 * x0 * (x2 - x0) * y1 + x0 * x1 * (x0 - x1) * y2) / denom;
474 
475  *xv = -b/(2*a);
476  *yv = c - b*b/(4*a);
477 }

496 static void DPC_ObjDet_rangeBiasRxChPhaseMeasure
497 (
498  DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,
499  float targetDistance,
500  float searchWinSize,
501  uint16_t *detMatrix,
502  uint32_t *symbolMatrix,
503  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *compRxChanCfg
504 )
505 {
506  cmplx16ImRe_t rxSym[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
507  cmplx16ImRe_t *tempPtr;
508  float sumSqr;
509  uint32_t * rxSymPtr = (uint32_t * ) rxSym;
510  float xMagSq[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
511  int32_t iMax;
512  float xMagSqMin;
513  float scal;
514  float truePosition;
515  int32_t truePositionIndex;
516  float y[3];
517  float x[3];
518  int32_t halfWinSize ;
519  float estPeakPos;
520  float estPeakVal;
521  int32_t i, ind;
522  int32_t txIdx, rxIdx;
523 
524  uint32_t numRxAntennas = staticCfg->ADCBufData.dataProperty.numRxAntennas;
525  uint32_t numTxAntennas = staticCfg->numTxAntennas;
526  uint32_t numRangeBins = staticCfg->numRangeBins;
527  uint32_t numDopplerChirps = staticCfg->numDopplerChirps;
528  uint32_t numSymPerTxAnt = numDopplerChirps * numRxAntennas * numRangeBins;
529  uint32_t symbolMatrixIndx;
530 
531  uint16_t maxVal = 0;
532 
533  truePosition = targetDistance / staticCfg->rangeStep;
534  truePositionIndex = (int32_t) (truePosition + 0.5);
535 
536  halfWinSize = (int32_t) (0.5 * searchWinSize / staticCfg->rangeStep + 0.5);
537 
538  /**** Range calibration ****/
539  iMax = truePositionIndex;
540  for (i = truePositionIndex - halfWinSize; i <= truePositionIndex + halfWinSize; i++)
541  {
542  if (detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins] > maxVal)
543  {
544  maxVal = detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins];
545  iMax = i;
546  }
547  }
548 
549  /* Fine estimate of the peak position using quadratic fit */
550  ind = 0;
551  for (i = iMax-1; i <= iMax+1; i++)
552  {
553  sumSqr = 0.0;
554  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
555  {
556  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
557  {
558  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + i;
559  tempPtr = (cmplx16ImRe_t *) &symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
560  sumSqr += (float) tempPtr->real * (float) tempPtr->real +
561  (float) tempPtr->imag * (float) tempPtr->imag;
562  }
563  }
564 #ifdef SUBSYS_DSS
565  y[ind] = sqrtsp(sumSqr);
566 #else
567  y[ind] = sqrt(sumSqr);
568 #endif
569  x[ind] = (float)i;
570  ind++;
571  }
572  DPC_ObjDet_quadFit(x, y, &estPeakPos, &estPeakVal);
573  compRxChanCfg->rangeBias = (estPeakPos - truePosition) * staticCfg->rangeStep;
574 
575  /*** Calculate Rx channel phase/gain compensation coefficients ***/
576  for (txIdx = 0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
577  {
578  for (rxIdx = 0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
579  {
580  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
581  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + iMax;
582  rxSymPtr[i] = symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
583  xMagSq[i] = (float) rxSym[i].real * (float) rxSym[i].real +
584  (float) rxSym[i].imag * (float) rxSym[i].imag;
585  }
586  }
587  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[0];
588  for (i = 1; i < staticCfg->numVirtualAntennas; i++)
589  {
590  if (xMagSq[i] < xMagSqMin)
591  {
592  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[i];
593  }
594  }
595 
596  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < staticCfg->numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
597  {
598  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
599  {
600  int32_t temp;
601  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
602  scal = 32768./ xMagSq[i] * sqrt(xMagSqMin);
603 
604  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(scal * rxSym[i].real);
605  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
606  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas +
607  rxIdx].real = (int16_t) (temp);
608 
609  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(-scal * rxSym[i].imag);
610  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
611  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas
612  + rxIdx].imag = (int16_t) (temp);
613  }
614  }
615 }

723  winType,
724  DPC_OBJDET_QFORMAT_DOPPLER_FFT);

743 static void DPC_ObjDet_GetRxChPhaseComp(DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,
744  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *inpCfg,
745  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *outCfg)
746 {
747  uint32_t tx, rx, numTxAnt, numRxAnt;
748  uint8_t *txAntOrder, *rxAntOrder;
749  cmplx16ImRe_t one;
750 
751  one.imag = 0;
752  one.real = 0x7fff;
753 
754  numTxAnt = staticCfg->numTxAntennas;
755  numRxAnt = staticCfg->ADCBufData.dataProperty.numRxAntennas;
756  txAntOrder = staticCfg->txAntOrder;
757  rxAntOrder = staticCfg->rxAntOrder;
758  outCfg->rangeBias = inpCfg->rangeBias;
759 
760  for(tx = 0; tx < numTxAnt; tx++)
761  {
762  for(rx = 0; rx < numRxAnt; rx++)
763  {
764  if (staticCfg->isValidProfileHasOneTxPerChirp == 1)
765  {
766  /* AOP ant: it will always come here
767  * STD ant: it will come here for MIMO cases
768  */
769  outCfg->rxChPhaseComp[tx * numRxAnt + rx] =
770  inpCfg->rxChPhaseComp[txAntOrder[tx] * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL +
771  rxAntOrder[rx]];
772  }
773  else
774  {
775  outCfg->rxChPhaseComp[tx * numRxAnt + rx] = one;
776  }
777  }
778  }
779 }

835 int32_t DPC_ObjectDetection_execute
836 (
837  DPM_DPCHandle handle,
838  DPM_Buffer* ptrResult
839 )
840 {
841  ObjDetObj *objDetObj;
842  SubFrameObj *subFrmObj;
843  DPU_RangeProcHWA_OutParams outRangeProc;
844  DPU_StaticClutterProc_OutParams outStaticClutter;
845  DPU_DopplerProcHWA_OutParams outDopplerProc;
846  DPU_CFARCAProcHWA_OutParams outCfarcaProc;
847  DPU_AoAProcHWA_OutParams outAoaProc;
848  int32_t retVal;
849  DPC_ObjectDetection_ExecuteResult *result;
850  DPC_ObjectDetection_ProcessCallBackCfg *processCallBack;
851  int32_t i;
852 
853  objDetObj = (ObjDetObj *) handle;
854  DebugP_assert (objDetObj != NULL);
855  DebugP_assert (ptrResult != NULL);
856 
857  DebugP_log1("ObjDet DPC: Processing sub-frame %d\n", objDetObj->subFrameIndx);
858 
859  processCallBack = &objDetObj->processCallBackCfg;

861  if (processCallBack->processFrameBeginCallBackFxn != NULL)

1085 static int32_t DPC_ObjectDetection_start (DPM_DPCHandle handle)
1086 {
1087  ObjDetObj *objDetObj;
1088  SubFrameObj *subFrmObj;
1089  int32_t retVal = 0;
1090 
1091  objDetObj = (ObjDetObj *) handle;
1092  DebugP_assert (objDetObj != NULL);
1093 
1094  objDetObj->stats.frameStartIntCounter = 0;
1095 
1096  /* Start marks consumption of all pre-start configs, reset the flag to check
1097  * if pre-starts were issued only after common config was issued for the next
1098  * time full configuration happens between stop and start */
1099  objDetObj->isCommonCfgReceived = false;
1100

1102  * so start should always see sub-frame indx of 0, check */
1103  DebugP_assert(objDetObj->subFrameIndx == 0);

1119  {
1120  goto exit;
1121  }
1122  }
1123 #endif

1126  if(retVal < 0)
1127  {
1128  goto exit;
1129  }
